\n<p class=\"center\">《方舟投資主禱文》<br />\n我們在天上的母：願人都尊契媽的名為聖。<br />\n願契媽的國降臨，願契媽的電動車馳騁在地上，<br />\n如同爆升在天上。我們盼望的升幅，<br />\n求契媽今日賜給我們，又求饒恕石仔拋售的罪，<br />\n因為我們饒恕得罪SH的人。<br />\n不叫我們遇見破壞性創新，拯救我們脫離短炒。<br />\n離開方舟的叛徒，定必受到地獄之火的懲罰。<br />\n因為坐貨、賺錢、移民，<br />\n全是契媽的子民，直到永遠。阿們。</p><br />\n<br />\nTrello 開左Public美股認真討論區 board，慢慢搬野上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F513A9wIT&d=oSiF6q%2BHtSOEBVfNLUnrLCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=5503793e\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT</a><br />\n<br />\nP巴貼紙登報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVCTV2q.jpg&amp;h=6266811b&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n開市前要唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vPKp29Luryc&amp;app=desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvPKp29Luryc%26app%3Ddesktop&d=oSiF6q%2BHtSOEBVfNLUnrLCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=eaefdb25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vPKp29Luryc&amp;app=desktop</a>"},{"pid":"8b5f67cb958c8fbb1e32fd78708c55008314df47","tid":2529593,"uid":358917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d1e9f3a67a04529ad54ba3b2e1791916fe3ac8","tid":2529593,"uid":57047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T18:04:58.000Z","msg":"This is the way"},{